{"tid":2240232,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"AO港台副處長指「無罪假定」再調查 利君雅質問高層：點解我變成受屈人？","createTime":"2020-10-12T13:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T14:07:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"086c0af9bd0ac5c96337490f59daa8507166898a","tid":2240232,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"香港電台《視點31》主持利君雅上月底被延長試用期120日，並重啟有關投訴她的調查。港台節目製作人員工會今召開員工大會，要求管方交代重啟調查的理據。工會會後指，負責重啟調查的副廣播處長馮建業說以「無罪假定」進行調查，批評馮的說法不妥。據了解，利君雅有出席大會並稱對事件感到含冤。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》獲悉，利君雅會上有發言，表示對事件感到含冤，直指負責處理重啟調查的馮建業「無罪假定」說法是詆毀她的人格及專業，亦批評事件顯然是程序失當。據悉利君雅會上說，涉及她的投訴更包括種族歧視，過去平機會都有出聲，質問：「你哋（管理層）有無為我主持公道？點解我變成受屈人？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/PX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FPX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU%2F&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=b4fa34d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FPX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU%2F&h=ff4fb650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/PX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU/</a>"},{"pid":"2fb9a1c276460fa729eb14f776c38e50bbf93b4e","tid":2240232,"uid":66049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"香港而家就係玩文革"},{"pid":"0285645ee465da231efe5a95cd43e29de238fdfb","tid":2240232,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:41:51.000Z","msg":"黨委書記好野"},{"pid":"7a9892449bd97580a9713dfeb5f8f87640941bf7","tid":2240232,"uid":56819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"真正種族歧視就唔出聲,支那人就話種族歧視,真係不知所謂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc87e332abd422a135ef436ecc4adda0c29456b","tid":2240232,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a